{"name":"Echarts基础图表工具","desc":"Echarts基础图表工具 饼状图、柱状图、折线图","code":"import com.alibaba.fastjson.JSONArray;\nimport com.alibaba.fastjson.JSONObject;\n\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.List;\n\n\npublic static String generateEChartsHtml(String xAxisStr, String yAxisStr, String chartTitle, String chartType) {\n// 1. 解析传入的JSON字符串为JSONArray\n// fastjson的parseArray方法可以直接将JSON字符串解析为JSONArray\nJSONArray xAxisData = JSONObject.parseArray(xAxisStr);\nJSONArray yAxisData = JSONObject.parseArray(yAxisStr);\n\n// 2. 构建 style 对象\nJSONObject style = new JSONObject();\nstyle.put(\"height\", \"400px\");\nstyle.put(\"width\", \"100%\");\n\n// 3. 构建 title 对象\nJSONObject title = new JSONObject();\ntitle.put(\"text\", chartTitle);\ntitle.put(\"left\", \"center\");\n\n// 4. 初始化 option 对象\nJSONObject option = new JSONObject();\noption.put(\"title\", title);\n\n// 5. 构建 series 对象\nJSONObject series = new JSONObject();\nseries.put(\"type\", chartType);\n\n// 6. 根据图表类型进行不同配置\nJSONObject tooltip = new JSONObject();\nif (!\"pie\".equals(chartType)) {\n// --- 非饼图配置 (如折线图、柱状图) ---\n\n// 配置 xAxis\nJSONObject xAxis = new JSONObject();\nxAxis.put(\"type\", \"category\");\nxAxis.put(\"boundaryGap\", false);\nxAxis.put(\"data\", xAxisData);\n\n// 配置 yAxis\nJSONObject yAxis = new JSONObject();\nyAxis.put(\"type\", \"value\");\n\n// 配置 markPoint (最大值/最小值)\nJSONObject markPointDataMax = new JSONObject();\nmarkPointDataMax.put(\"type\", \"max\");\nmarkPointDataMax.put(\"name\", \"最大值\");\n\nJSONObject markPointDataMin = new JSONObject();\nmarkPointDataMin.put(\"type\", \"min\");\nmarkPointDataMin.put(\"name\", \"最小值\");\n\nJSONArray markPointDataArray = new JSONArray();\nmarkPointDataArray.add(markPointDataMax);\nmarkPointDataArray.add(markPointDataMin);\n\nJSONObject onlineMarkPoint = new JSONObject();\nonlineMarkPoint.put(\"data\", markPointDataArray);\n\n// 组装 series\nseries.put(\"data\", yAxisData);\nseries.put(\"markPoint\", onlineMarkPoint);\n\n// 将 xAxis 和 yAxis 添加到 option\noption.put(\"xAxis\", xAxis);\noption.put(\"yAxis\", yAxis);\n\n// 设置 tooltip 触发方式\ntooltip.put(\"trigger\", \"axis\");\n\n} else {\n// --- 饼图配置 ---\n\nJSONArray seriesData = new JSONArray();\n// 注意：这里假设xAxisData和yAxisData的长度是一致的\nfor (int i = 0; i < xAxisData.size(); i++) {\n    JSONObject dataItem = new JSONObject();\n    dataItem.put(\"value\", yAxisData.get(i));\n    dataItem.put(\"name\", xAxisData.get(i));\n    seriesData.add(dataItem);\n}\nseries.put(\"data\", seriesData);\n\n// 设置 tooltip 触发方式\ntooltip.put(\"trigger\", \"item\");\n}\n\n// 7. 将 tooltip 和 series 添加到 option\noption.put(\"tooltip\", tooltip);\nJSONArray seriesArray = new JSONArray();\nseriesArray.add(series);\noption.put(\"series\", seriesArray);\n\n// 8. 构建最终的 formSetting 对象\nJSONObject formSetting = new JSONObject();\nformSetting.put(\"actionType\", \"JSON\");\nformSetting.put(\"style\", style);\nformSetting.put(\"option\", option);\n\n// 9. 将最终对象转换为字符串并包装在HTML标签中\n// JSON.toJSONString() 会将对象序列化为JSON字符串\nreturn \"<echarts_render>\" + JSONObject.toJSONString(formSetting) + \"</echarts_render>\";\n}\n\nreturn generateEChartsHtml(xAxisStr,yAxisStr,chartTitle,chartType)","inputFieldList":[{"name":"chartTitle","type":"string","source":"reference","isRequired":true},{"name":"xAxisStr","type":"string","source":"reference","isRequired":true},{"name":"yAxisStr","type":"string","source":"reference","isRequired":true}],"initFieldList":[{"field":"chartType","option_list":[{"label":"折线图","value":"line"},{"label":"柱状图","value":"bar"},{"label":"饼图","value":"pie"}],"input_type":"SingleSelect","text_field":"label","value_field":"value","default_value":"line","label":{"input_type":"TooltipLabel","label":"chartType","props_info":{},"attrs":{"tooltip":"图表类型"}},"required":true,"show_default_value":true,"attrs":{}}],"initParams":{"chartType":"line"},"userId":"09e46b174171ebc86ac46a6dc9da12cd","isActive":true,"toolType":"CUSTOM","label":"developer","scope":"WORKSPACE","icon":"./tool/echarts/icon.png","templateId":"","folderId":"default","version":"","id":"2e95b0643b49681722060029fb57363e","createTime":1769648342000,"updateTime":1775626687578}